[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2095[0m:[38;5;10m[49m **Step 7: Generate care-team reports and run the outcome-correlation pipeline.** The care team has visibility into the assistant's activity through real-time alerts, weekly digests, monthly summaries, transition-of-care closure reports, and quarterly clinical-review packets. The outcome-correlation pipeline correlates coordination metrics with clinical and utilization outcomes (referral closure rate, transition-of-care completion rate, medication-reconciliation accuracy, readmission rate, ED-utilization rate, total cost of care). Skip the reporting and the care team has no visibility; skip the outcome correlation and the program runs without evidence of effect.
